title: Real Madrid full-back Danilo shows off horror leg scars after accidental stamp in victory over Osasuna but his opponent suffered worse
text:
EFL WAR WOUNDS Real Madrid full-back Danilo shows off horror leg scars after accidental stamp in victory over Osasuna but his opponent suffered worse 
Osasuna centre-back Tano Bonnin suffered a far worse fate though, breaking his leg in two places as Real went on to win 3-1 Pictured
